0010 REM "SYM - Process Maintenance (Definition)"
0020 REM "Program SYM.IB"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0 - 15May96 |"
